text: Eerland in 2016 Britt Eerland (born 22 February 1994) is a Dutch table tennis player. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics as part of the Dutch team in the women's team event. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of the Netherlands Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Table tennis players at the 2010 Summer Youth Olympics Category:European Games medalists in table tennis Category:European Games competitors for the Netherlands Category:Table tennis players at the 2015 European Games Category:Table tennis players at the 2019 European Games Category:European Games silver medalists for the Netherlands
